      "content": "talking to someone wont change anyting. they dont get it. they just tell me to \"ignore it\" or \"be brave\" but it doesnt stop the notifications on my phone or the looks in the hallway. it feels like no matter what i do, i'm just stuck in this loop of being hated. there is literally no way out of this feeling. it's just permanent.",
